Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.48,0:00:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Coppelia之柩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.61,0:00:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,流下的泪水早已干枯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.82,0:00:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,对血感到饥渴的孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡散发着\N{\fs8}\N{\r}天使柔和羽毛气息飞舞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.57,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗太阳不西沉的街道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.97,0:00:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,任谁都沉默不语
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.98,0:00:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,仿佛奇术般的运转
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.41,0:00:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,见不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.05,0:00:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里见不到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,能够拯救我们的神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:00:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Coppelia之柩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:01:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,人们是疲惫的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.44,0:01:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,祭坛的羔羊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.67,0:01:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,机械梦想究竟朝向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.65,0:01:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Coppelia之柩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.78,0:01:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,从黑暗苏醒的光芒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.92,0:01:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,祭坛的羔羊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.12,0:01:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,螺丝中断的梦想究竟朝向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Noir
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,其乃自古命运之名
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,掌管死亡的两名少女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.28,0:01:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗圣手诱使迷途者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,坠入业火深渊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:25.02,Title,,0,0,0,,#25 业火之渊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,仪式马上就要准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你们成为真正NOlR\N{\fs8}\N{\r}的时刻终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.85,0:02:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-是的\N{\fs8}\N{\r}-是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.02,0:03:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,为了让你们两人\N{\fs8}\N{\r}清净身体、加强牵绊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.26,0:03:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,必须进行圣灵仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,让我仔细看看你们两人的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.48,0:03:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,艾尔黛娜，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,能得到你的疼爱，我很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是啊，克洛维
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,真正的NOlR
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,受灵魂牵绊而结合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:05:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,誓言一同存活于黑暗的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,时候终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,被时间遗忘的这个场所
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.44,0:06:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,将改变今后的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,已经无人能阻挡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,雾香…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这里不是你该来的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,米雷优就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.72,0:11:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,雾香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.61,0:12:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,仪式马上就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让任何人来妨碍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.02,0:12:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,即使是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这孩子的朋友也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.62,0:13:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,米雷优就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你和米雷优
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,今后一定会面对痛苦的试炼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.24,0:13:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,请你一定要帮助那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,的确有时会因为爱而杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但是，不要忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.68,0:13:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,憎恨是绝对救不了人的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,憎恨…是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,憎恨是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,无法…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,救人…的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这个地方在过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是殉于黑暗的少女们\N{\fs8}\N{\r}较劲彼此的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,并选出真正NOlR的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你死在这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,也可说是…命运
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.79,0:14:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,米雷优．布克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你骗人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这样，克洛维
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,看到在巴黎生活的你和米雷优
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,让我感到非常…非常…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那明明应该是我的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.69,0:16:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,明明应该是我才对！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你，克洛维
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.11,0:16:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不要再这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,克洛维
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,克洛维！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.68,0:18:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,NOlR…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,克洛维是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.51,0:19:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,另一个我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.52,0:19:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我能够杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.03,0:19:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,杀人之后，我会感到悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.77,0:20:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么…会变成这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧，雾香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,还没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:20:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,米雷优
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,米雷优…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.28,0:21:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧，雾香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.62,0:22:34.32,ED,,0,0,0,,轻轻地被触碰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.39,0:22:46.93,ED,,0,0,0,,终于察觉到脸颊的冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.01,0:22:52.81,ED,,0,0,0,,清晨醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.88,0:23:05.22,ED,,0,0,0,,突然开始注意到鸟鸣声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.29,0:23:09.99,ED,,0,0,0,,什么都还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.43,0:23:20.77,ED,,0,0,0,,不知内心追求的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.84,0:23:25.80,ED,,0,0,0,,总是望着天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:33.05,ED,,0,0,0,,不知何时开始这样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.12,0:23:46.12,ED,,0,0,0,,让思念朝着云的下方飞去
